It’s just as a by-product as you get rid
of your troubles.

00:42:08.150 --> 00:42:13.590
In the same way, these habits also drop out.

00:42:13.590 --> 00:42:20.010
You become independent you become free not
slave of anything because you are the Spirit

00:42:20.010 --> 00:42:22.300
which is the freedom within you.

00:42:22.300 --> 00:42:25.030
Complete supreme freedom is your Spirit.

00:42:25.030 --> 00:42:36.160
Last of all, I will tell you about a horrible
disease, which is the modern disease nowadays,

00:42:36.160 --> 00:42:42.090
is the disease of cancer, which is a horrible
thing as people say.

00:42:42.090 --> 00:42:49.740
Cancer is caused mostly, which I have seen,
in the people who are left-sided.

00:42:49.740 --> 00:42:53.760
Not so much in the right-sided people, those
who are aggressive.

00:42:53.760 --> 00:42:56.880
But those who are emotionally ones disturbed
get this trouble.

00:42:56.880 --> 00:43:04.650
So far, I have not seen one patient of cancer
who has not been emotionally very much inclined.

00:43:04.650 --> 00:43:12.730
It might look, appear that a person is very
aggressive, but if you really go into the

00:43:12.730 --> 00:43:19.120
history of a person you will find that he
had a problem, that his mother died, or his

00:43:19.120 --> 00:43:24.710
father died early, or some sort of an emotional
problem he developed later on, or a shock

00:43:24.710 --> 00:43:29.610
from his wife or a fiancée, from his children
or something like that.

00:43:29.610 --> 00:43:35.210
It’s more a case of emotional disturbance.

00:43:35.210 --> 00:43:43.360
Now when you find, that a person has a cancer,
on the hands you’ll find that all these

00:43:43.360 --> 00:43:45.080
fingers are burning [Shri Mataji shows all
the fingers of Her left hand], sometimes even

00:43:45.080 --> 00:43:46.930
these fingers start burning [Shri Mataji shows
fingers of Her right hand].

00:43:46.930 --> 00:43:54.190
When it is on a galloping state you put your
hands towards a person who is suffering from

00:43:54.190 --> 00:43:59.020
cancer- even doctors might not diagnose it,
they might find it later on – all your fingers

00:43:59.020 --> 00:44:00.140
start burning.

00:44:00.140 --> 00:44:05.320
You start burning here and here [Shri Mataji
points on the top of the palm near the fingers].

00:44:05.320 --> 00:44:06.650
Also, you may start feeling a throbbing here
[Shri Mataji points to the solar plexus].

00:44:06.650 --> 00:44:14.340
Of course, throbbing doesn’t mean that a
person has a cancer, but is one of the symptoms.

00:44:14.340 --> 00:44:16.330
Now how cancer is caused?

00:44:16.330 --> 00:44:17.330
It’s very simple.

00:44:17.330 --> 00:44:22.710
And to understand it- it’s better that if
you understand- you will not those things

00:44:22.710 --> 00:44:24.740
which are not to be done.

00:44:24.740 --> 00:44:30.730
Anything we do into extremes, I mean any emergency
is taking over by this two sides, because

00:44:30.730 --> 00:44:33.720
they manifest the sympathetic nervous system.

00:44:33.720 --> 00:44:37.370
They act for our sympathetic nervous system
whenever there is an emergency.

00:44:37.370 --> 00:44:43.170
For example, a person has a habit, a simple
habit, of say, rubbing his ears, very simple

00:44:43.170 --> 00:44:44.170
habit.

00:44:44.170 --> 00:44:45.530
He may develop a cancer there.

00:44:45.530 --> 00:44:47.310
Because he has overdone it.

00:44:47.310 --> 00:44:50.480
An extreme thing he has done is rubbing, rubbing,
rubbing.

00:44:50.480 --> 00:44:57.080
So, what happens is that the cells which are
supported by a centre here, for example, it’s

00:44:57.080 --> 00:44:58.970
coming from left and right [Shri Mataji forms
a triangle to mime the spinal cord] – and

00:44:58.970 --> 00:45:00.080
that’s how a centre is formed.

00:45:00.080 --> 00:45:01.820
If you can see all of you.

00:45:01.820 --> 00:45:06.520
This is the one through which the medulla
oblongata passes, the spinal cord, this is

00:45:06.520 --> 00:45:07.780
the spinal cord.

00:45:07.780 --> 00:45:13.630
Now, when there is a pull on right-side or
left-side too much, on the sympathetic nervous

00:45:13.630 --> 00:45:17.760
system, then this connection breaks out like
that [Shri Mataji splits the hands].

00:45:17.760 --> 00:45:22.900
When it breaks out the connection of the centre
with the whole, because this centre [right

00:45:22.900 --> 00:45:25.100
thumb] is supplying the energy, is broken.

00:45:25.100 --> 00:45:31.530
When the connection with the whole is broken,
there is no coordination left, there is no

00:45:31.530 --> 00:45:32.530
control left.

00:45:32.530 --> 00:45:37.170
So, the cells become on their own what we
call malignant.

00:45:37.170 --> 00:45:38.440
They start growing on their own.

00:45:38.440 --> 00:45:42.230
For example, if their nose develops the cancer,
than nose becomes big.

00:45:42.230 --> 00:45:49.340
The rest of the- is smaller and the cells
of the nose start pressing all other organs

00:45:49.340 --> 00:45:50.620
in here [on the throat].

00:45:50.620 --> 00:45:54.680
And sometimes they may pass into blood and
go to other areas also.

00:45:54.680 --> 00:45:59.920
So, these are aggressive cells, malignant
cells are on their own, you cannot control

00:45:59.920 --> 00:46:00.920
them.

00:46:00.920 --> 00:46:07.420
By some chance, if you could bring them back
in connection with the whole, if you can do

00:46:07.420 --> 00:46:09.100
that, cancer can be cured.

00:46:09.100 --> 00:46:10.780
It’s as simple as that.

00:46:10.780 --> 00:46:15.130
When the Kundalini rises, what she does is,
she awakens the centre.

00:46:15.130 --> 00:46:20.670
And when the centre is awakened, it just comes
back to normal and a person becomes normal.

00:46:20.670 --> 00:46:22.650
That’s how cancer can be cured.

00:46:22.650 --> 00:46:25.110
It is very simple, it’s not so difficult.

00:46:25.110 --> 00:46:29.710
Human life we have made it so difficult, actually
it’s not so difficult.

00:46:29.710 --> 00:46:37.181
It’s a very simple thing if you understand
the laws of nature and laws of God’s divine

00:46:37.181 --> 00:46:38.181
Power.

