01:10:08.710 --> 01:10:09.710
your being.

01:10:09.710 --> 01:10:15.360
I have seen another television show where
they showed Gogin entering into somebody.

01:10:15.360 --> 01:10:16.900
And he was painting just like him.

01:10:16.900 --> 01:10:22.170
The lines were just like him, bold the same
wave very different styles that he has.

01:10:22.170 --> 01:10:24.610
And he was doing it and he said: ‘I’m
Gogin.’

01:10:24.610 --> 01:10:27.110
And this is very common even with curatives.

01:10:27.110 --> 01:10:30.600
When people cured, they use spiritualists.

01:10:30.600 --> 01:10:32.350
That’s very dangerous.

01:10:32.350 --> 01:10:37.160
All these are taking you to the realm, which
is not your own.

01:10:37.160 --> 01:10:39.190
It is somebody else who acts in you.

01:10:39.190 --> 01:10:44.560
Even a thing like, say acupuncture can be
very dangerous, because acupuncture uses the

01:10:44.560 --> 01:10:48.440
whatever energy in you of the sympathetic.

01:10:48.440 --> 01:10:51.050
This is energy I’m talking which is all
the time flowing.

01:10:51.050 --> 01:10:53.960
When you get connected with the mains all
the time it is flowing within you.

01:10:53.960 --> 01:10:57.450
That’s the energy we should have.

01:10:57.450 --> 01:11:00.090
And the scientists are correct when they say
vibrations.

01:11:00.090 --> 01:11:01.360
But they can’t say, why there are vibrations.

01:11:01.360 --> 01:11:04.210
This is the point.

01:11:04.210 --> 01:11:10.730
Not that I’m against science because today
the science is helping us so much.

01:11:10.730 --> 01:11:25.460
Man ask about his son, which have skin problems.

01:11:25.460 --> 01:11:27.100
[analogous]

01:11:27.100 --> 01:11:42.900
Shri Mataji: Ah, skin problem.

01:11:42.900 --> 01:11:51.230
All right, there’s nothing, that’s liver.

01:11:51.230 --> 01:12:01.239
Woman: How can I help myself…

01:12:01.239 --> 01:12:16.250
Sahaja Yogi: How can she learn to cure herself.

01:12:16.250 --> 01:12:28.580
Shri Mataji: Yes, that’s what I’m saying
that today if you get Realization well and

01:12:28.580 --> 01:12:29.580
good.

01:12:29.580 --> 01:12:31.469
Otherwise there is a centre, you can come,
by which whatever you have cured yourself,

01:12:31.469 --> 01:12:32.469
but you can cure others also.

01:12:32.469 --> 01:12:33.469
[1:06:59]

01:12:33.469 --> 01:12:34.469
Man: The Self-realization, Sahaja Yoga.

01:12:34.469 --> 01:12:43.880
Is that the answer about our problems?

01:12:43.880 --> 01:12:45.520
[… some words unclear]

01:12:45.520 --> 01:12:51.230
Shri Mataji: Hundred percent, to all problems.

01:12:51.230 --> 01:12:53.630
You see, because we live in a relative world.

01:12:53.630 --> 01:12:57.650
We are living relatively and we are confused,
isn’t it?

01:12:57.650 --> 01:13:00.330
But when you find the absolute, all the questions
are solved.

01:13:00.330 --> 01:13:05.530
That’s true, because spirit is to be awakened,
that’s the main thing.

01:13:05.530 --> 01:13:06.790
Spirit is the solution.

01:13:06.790 --> 01:13:09.750
Firstly, it is the collective being.

01:13:09.750 --> 01:13:13.840
Again, it is the source of all vitality.

01:13:13.840 --> 01:13:16.440
It is the source of all the creativity.

01:13:16.440 --> 01:13:21.510
It is the source of all the joy and bliss.

01:13:21.510 --> 01:13:26.661
Once you achieve that being within you, when
that being shines in your attention, you become

01:13:26.661 --> 01:13:31.550
the master of that.

01:13:31.550 --> 01:13:37.840
[1:08:03] Woman: Question incomprehensible.

01:13:37.840 --> 01:13:48.850
Shri Mataji: Can you say it loudly?

01:13:48.850 --> 01:14:03.900
Man: She says Mother, has the mother nature
provided the answer in terms of herbs to cure

01:14:03.900 --> 01:14:04.900
people?

01:14:04.900 --> 01:14:10.760
Shri Mataji: We don’t use any herbs or anything.

01:14:10.760 --> 01:14:16.650
We at the most can sanctify some water or
salt or sugar, these basic things, that’s

01:14:16.650 --> 01:14:17.650
all.

01:14:17.650 --> 01:14:21.020
We don’t use any herbs or anything, that’s
not needed now anymore.

01:14:21.020 --> 01:14:29.330
Woman: Excuse me, do we have to be religious
to… [some words incomprehensible]

01:14:29.330 --> 01:14:33.070
Shri Mataji: You don’t have to be religious
at all.

01:14:33.070 --> 01:14:35.310
But religious is different from religion!

01:14:35.310 --> 01:14:38.820
Religion is within you, you can’t get rid
of it.

01:14:38.820 --> 01:14:42.440
You see, religion is your quality as a human
being.

01:14:42.440 --> 01:14:45.239
That’s within you, you can’t get rid of
it.

01:14:45.239 --> 01:14:51.170
If you go against it, whatever is within you,
then there is a problem.

01:14:51.170 --> 01:14:52.170
Yes, everyone has that, everyone has that!

01:14:52.170 --> 01:14:54.360
That’s true and that’s why you get problems.

01:14:54.360 --> 01:14:56.870
But religious is a very absurd thing.

01:14:56.870 --> 01:15:02.100
Sometimes religious so called people can be
horridly hot tempered, you know.

01:15:02.100 --> 01:15:07.310
Could be very bad and could be – I mean,
it has no relationship whit reality sometimes.

01:15:07.310 --> 01:15:14.230
So religious is a different thing, but religion
is important.

01:15:14.230 --> 01:15:22.530
Religion is universal, which is within you.

01:15:22.530 --> 01:15:27.280
Now, let’s start now.

01:15:27.280 --> 01:15:32.030
Woman: Question about diet.

01:15:32.030 --> 01:15:35.590
[exact wording unclear]

01:15:35.590 --> 01:15:49.820
Man: She says Mother, does the diet which
we … solve her problems?

01:15:49.820 --> 01:15:56.870
Shri Mataji: Yes, not the diet want solve
it completely, but when you take to Sahaja

01:15:56.870 --> 01:15:58.860
Yoga, supposing you are a liver-patient, all
right.

01:15:58.860 --> 01:16:04.900
So, we give you some sanctified or vibrated
sugar to eat, white sugar.

01:16:04.900 --> 01:16:08.900
Now doctors will say: “Don’t eat white
sugar”, but we have cured so many of liver

01:16:08.900 --> 01:16:09.900
troubles.

01:16:09.900 --> 01:16:14.730
All have migraines and this and that and so
many troubles of the allergies are to be cured.

01:16:14.730 --> 01:16:18.330
Now for that of course we say, for about a
month, you just don’t eat some fats.

01:16:18.330 --> 01:16:19.350
You see, that’s all right.

01:16:19.350 --> 01:16:24.340
But that by eating, you see, you paying so
much attention ‘eat this, eat that!

01:16:24.340 --> 01:16:26.020
That food, that food!’

01:16:26.020 --> 01:16:27.020
That’s not needed.

01:16:27.020 --> 01:16:29.570
It’s too much attention diverted to food.

01:16:29.570 --> 01:16:30.730
But you should know basics.

01:16:30.730 --> 01:16:33.420
But if this is the problem with you then what
you should eat.

01:16:33.420 --> 01:16:39.130
That’s all, it’s not such a emphasis on
diet that you eat this.

01:16:39.130 --> 01:16:43.020
Only by dieting you maybe, all right, at the
most physically, but you are not only a physical

01:16:43.020 --> 01:16:44.050
being.

01:16:44.050 --> 01:16:46.150
You are also an emotional being.

01:16:46.150 --> 01:16:49.380
If you pay too much attention to your physical
side, you can become a dry personality.

01:16:49.380 --> 01:16:50.380
Absolutely.

01:16:50.380 --> 01:16:56.300
There could be divorces in the families and
such a person who just is nothing but a physical,

01:16:56.300 --> 01:16:57.300
imagine.

01:16:57.300 --> 01:17:04.300
It can be very dangerous and can be a very,
very angry person who has just physical thing.

01:17:04.300 --> 01:17:10.520
And such a person gets heart – heart trouble,
because the spirit resides in your heart and

01:17:10.520 --> 01:17:15.230
if you are too much physical, then the heart
goes out, because you must pay attention to

01:17:15.230 --> 01:17:16.230
your spirit.

01:17:16.230 --> 01:18:17.300
So, you are not only a physical being, you
are a mental being, you

01:18:17.300 --> 01:19:44.090
are an emotional being
and you

01:19:44.090 --> 01:20:03.290
are

01:20:03.290 --> 01:20:14.110
a spiritual being.

01:20:14.110 --> 01:22:32.900
All

01:22:32.900 --> 01:22:44.590
this

01:22:44.590 --> 01:23:32.100
must

01:23:32.100 --> 01:31:17.860
be integrated and there should be

01:31:17.860 --> 01:37:00.610
a complete balance.
